Changelog
=========

2.8.0 (2019-12-05)
------------------

- Look for isort configuration on `.flake8` files as well.
  [JohnHBrock]

- Document how to install `flake8-isort` on conda.
  [marcelotrevisani]

- Look for isort configuration on `pyproject.toml` files as well.
  [sanjioh]


